author: Ethem Alpaydin
title: Combined 5 x 2 cv F Test for Comparing Supervised Classification Learning Algorithms
window: 2 no VOWEL 2 no ODR 8 yes DIGIT 7 yes PEN 10 yes changing the numerator where we compare a single layer perceptron (LP) with a multilayer perceptron with one hidden layer (MLP). ODR, DIGIT are two datasets on optical handwritten digit recognition and PEN is on pen-based handwritten digit recognition. These three datasets are available from the author. The other datasets are from the UCI repository
